---

Features
	1.	Episode Story Flow:
	◦	Generate episodic content with scenes and character actions.
	2.	Visual Generation:
	◦	Batch image creation with Anime-style outputs.
	◦	Image-to-video pipeline with frame interpolation.
	3.	Audio Integration:
	◦	AI-generated voice narration.
	◦	Automatic background music and SFX addition.
	4.	Video Publishing:
	◦	Simple video editing integration.
	◦	Direct upload to YouTube.

---

Technical Implementation
	1.	Backend API for AI Inference:
	◦	Integrate Hugging Face Spaces.
	◦	GPU acceleration for model execution.
	2.	React App Extensions:
	◦	Batch image uploads.
	◦	Prediction grid display.
	◦	Real-time confidence bar visualization.
	3.	Performance Optimization:
	◦	Local model caching.
	◦	Faster switching between models.

---

CLI Commands
	•	init-episode – Initialize new episode structure.
	•	generate-scenes – Run scene generator and planner.
	•	render-images – Produce AI-based Anime images.
	•	build-episode – Combine video, audio, and narration.
	•	publish – Upload final episode to YouTube.

---

This documentation provides a clear pipeline from text prompts to a fully published episode, including backend integration and frontend enhancements.

